AgenticAI-Daily/
│
├── agents/                     ← AI brains (logic)
│   ├── ai_topic_generator.py   ← Picks unique AI topics daily
│   ├── ai_content_agent.py     ← Writes full blog posts
│   └── daily_update.py         ← Runs everything (main file)
│
├── content/                    ← Hugo content
│   └── posts/                  ← Generated blog posts (.md)
│       ├── 2026-01-28-AI-Agent-Tools.md
│       ├── 2026-01-29-Automation-for-Business.md
│       └── ...
│
├── templates/                  ← Blog post structure
│   └── post_template.md        ← Markdown layout
│
├── config/                     ← Configuration
│   ├── config.json             ← Groq API key + model
│   └── used_topics.json        ← Prevents duplicate topics
│
├── themes/                     ← Hugo theme
│   └── ananke/                 ← Theme files (downloaded)
│
├── static/                     ← Images, logos (optional)
│
├── hugo.toml                   ← Hugo site config
├── requirements.txt            ← Python dependencies
└── README.md                   ← How to run (instructions)
